Package org.sibermatica.io.file

Class FilesUncheck

java.lang.Object
org.sibermatica.io.file.FilesUncheck
public final class FilesUncheck extends Object
Delegates to Files to uncheck calls by throwing UncheckedIOException instead of IOException.
Since:
2.12.0
See Also:
Files, IOException, UncheckedIOException
